    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU1 is accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels at MRL 2. The discretization error factor achieved Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3; this gap was considered acceptable given the conservative hemolysis power-law exponent used and the margin observed in output comparison results. Overall model credibility is judged sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission.",
